{"tid":1140772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳特朗普貼文假截圖　訛稱下輪加徵關稅包括香港","createTime":"2019-05-06T05:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T16:44:38.000Z","uid":54870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e629f2fae53795da0c4a8b7a12592f0e06c0408b","tid":1140772,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普宣布，決定本周五（10日）向中國價值2000億美元（約1.56萬億港元）商品所徵的關稅，由原本的10%增至25%，引起市場波動。網上流傳一張假截圖，訛稱下輪加徵關稅將包括香港。<br />\n<br />\n該張截圖偽造成從美國總統特朗普的Twitter貼文截下，上面以英文寫道：「我不接受重新談判！將會推出加徵更多關稅措施，之後將會包括香港。」惟記者前往特朗普的官方Twitter查看時，並未找到該則假貼文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYbaMab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYbaMab.jpg&h=f91a1583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190506/bkn-20190506114447218-0506_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1i3qEMzexKvAC8MAHaqilJNJ4SL2Iq3z9Xbwvt53RQURWm2FPU32Coj4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190506%2Fbkn-20190506114447218-0506_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1i3qEMzexKvAC8MAHaqilJNJ4SL2Iq3z9Xbwvt53RQURWm2FPU32Coj4s&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkNyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=d102eef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190506/bkn-20190506114447218-0506_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1i3qEMzexKvAC8MAHaqilJNJ4SL2Iq3z9Xbwvt53RQURWm2FPU32Coj4s</a>"},{"pid":"4aa0aee6e01b9dc4acbdcf65402fdb5147a79e8f","tid":1140772,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港爆"},{"pid":"3d925dbe4f5c5910df76882b8384c30a67d860e3","tid":1140772,"uid":550,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"反而東方識得fact check<br />\n傑斯條廢老中撚咗伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces